{"tid":1282430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔教育下中國人？","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T17:44:21.000Z","uid":222614,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bc913e1c59990928a3f5cda124bf900ffe5391f2","tid":1282430,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"已知本香港每日不斷有大量中國遊客<br />\n何不教育佢地，向佢地展示咩係言論自由，集會自由？展示香港人與中國人之別！<br />\n<br />\n已知佢地好鐘意我地既銅鑼灣<br />\n何不趁假日，佢地聚集銅鑼灣時幫佢地上自由既一課？<br />\n話唔定佢地受到如斯文化衝擊，返到本國會有所不同<br />\n<br />\n何不於本周六日，萬人包圍銅鑼灣？"},{"pid":"24a3a3231838ba810df8b2a860102eb039999534","tid":1282430,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:41:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"34307a05b4c70aba2f437ff462631a0585bfef79","tid":1282430,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a266674b8454e773132433f5e37f2a5944d3f61f","tid":1282430,"uid":90946,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:43:01.000Z","msg":"佢地就算知咩事<br />\n都唔會敢出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸個結界勁過西貢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3e98f0702718209ea9ba5947f993d48fb11416","tid":1282430,"uid":152759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"共產黨由佢地一出世就開始洗佢地腦 改變係需要時間 一時三刻改變唔到 除非佢地長期居住係民主社會慢慢同化"},{"pid":"629cc569b67773665e537fce9be7b6888afdd83a","tid":1282430,"uid":48379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"屋企啲廢中都教唔聽<br />\n點教中國人?"},{"pid":"9b03df1fd04f1f212dd02f2ed0cd4c89bc0723dd","tid":1282430,"uid":45007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"大城市個d比人圈養慣左 唔會有用<br />\n小城市人數唔夠 但其實經常有<br />\n但中共好快和諧左"},{"pid":"6ff293226166453512f408e30bcc0cdc965b826d","tid":1282430,"uid":222614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a266674b8